snippet.title: Troublemaker - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Hello geng! We have some very exciting news!
Class starts on March 31th - that’s when Troublemaker will launch on on PC! 🎉
Thank you all for your support throughout development! We could not have done it without your support. 

While you wait for Troublemaker to launch, you can join our community on Discord or follow us on Twitter! 
https://bit.ly/troublemakergame

Stay cool, Stay UwU everyone!
